@startuml
actor "Admin" as A
participant "Frontend" as F
participant "Stats API" as API
database "MongoDB" as DB

A -> F: Mở tab Thống Kê
F -> API: GET /api/admin/stats
API -> DB: Aggregate Bookings by Status (Pending, Confirmed, Cancelled)
DB --> API: statusCounts
API -> DB: Aggregate Revenue by Date/Month
DB --> API: revenueData
API -> DB: Aggregate Top Services Booked
DB --> API: serviceStats
API --> F: 200 OK {statusCounts, revenueData, serviceStats}
F -> F: Render Recharts (BarChart, PieChart)
F --> A: Màn hình trực quan
@enduml
